This project implements AES-128 cipher in CBC mode in Go Language.

It uses the following crypto packages:
crypto/aes
crypto/rand
crypto/sha256

The command line usahe is as follows:


./encrypt-auth <mode> -k <32-byte key in hexadecimal> -i <input filename> -o <output filename>

Here mode can be set to: "encrypt" or "decrypt"


==============================================================================================================

Usage of testing harness script:

./testing_harness ./encrypt-auth <plaintext filename> <ciphertext filename> <recovered plaintext filename>


